title: Custom Hooks
content: Custom hooks are a powerful way to reuse stateful logic across multiple components. They allow you to extract component logic into reusable functions.

title: What is the main purpose of a reducer?|To specify how state changes|To hold state|To dispatch actions
Pandas DataFrames
content: DataFrames are the primary data structure in Pandas. They are two-dimensional, size-mutable, and potentially heterogeneous tabular data structures with labeled axes (rows and columns).
